rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0001
rows.name: All right, everybody, dig in![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0002
rows.name: And don't hold back—I made enough for everyone![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0003
rows.name: Tatsu helped with cooking, too![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0004
rows.name: Wow—you really went all out![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0005
rows.name:
It smells amazing.
...Don't go hogging it all, Gwin.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0006
rows.name: Yeah, whatever. You're one to talk. Er...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0007
rows.name: How kind of you to dessert us like this, Lin![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0008
rows.name:
What in the HELL is this?!
We're going to WAR here, people.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0009
rows.name:
And you know what they say:
can't go to war on an empty stomach.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0010
rows.name:
Can't go to war if you're dead, either!
Which is us if the Lifehold's power runs out.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0011
rows.name:
For all we know, the Ganglion are already at the core,
getting ready to tear it apart![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0012
rows.name: You still hungry?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0014
rows.name: If we lose this one battle, we lose EVERYTHING.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0015
rows.name:
We already understand that, Doug.
But you heard what Nagi said.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0016
rows.name: We have to wait while they pinpoint the Core's location.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0017
rows.name: Like this?! You just don't get it, do you?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0018
rows.name: No, Doug—YOU don't get it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0019
rows.name: What?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0020
rows.name:
You think you're the only one here who's worried?
We all are. We're scared to death![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0021
rows.name: That's why we're here.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0022
rows.name: Together.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0023
rows.name: Look, Irina—[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0024
rows.name:
Lin is just trying to keep up morale
the best way she knows how.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0025
rows.name: Yeah—pick on Linly and you answer to Tatsu![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0027
rows.name: All right. Look, Lin... I'm sorry.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0028
rows.name: I'm on edge. Worried. Freaked out—all of it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0029
rows.name: Forgive me, okay?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0030
rows.name: No, but bring me 10 hot cocoas...and we'll talk.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0031
rows.name:
Heh. From that place you love, right?
Okay, you got it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_JNK0010
rows.name: Relax

rows.label: xs12020100_SEL0011
rows.name: Enjoy this time with friends.

rows.label: xs12020100_JNK0020
rows.name: Chow Down

rows.label: xs12020100_SEL0021
rows.name: Dive right in and start eating.

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0032
rows.name:
All right, everyone, Lin went to all this trouble,
so let's dig in before it gets cold.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0033
rows.name: Tatsu like this plan! Tatsu is starving![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0034
rows.name: Well, you don't have to ask me twice.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0035
rows.name: Whoa-whoa-whoa![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0036
rows.name: Hey, wait for us![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0037
rows.name: Save some for Tatsu![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0038
rows.name: Help yourself, Doug.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0039
rows.name: Heh. Roger that.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0040
rows.name: Oh man, am I stuffed![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0041
rows.name: I couldn't eat another bite.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0042
rows.name: Tatsu. Cannot. Move.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0043
rows.name: Amazing as always, Lin. Thank you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0044
rows.name:
Now I get why Irina and the Commander
are always making excuses to swing by.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0045
rows.name: That was delicious, Lin.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0046
rows.name: Oh, you guys.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0047
rows.name: Don't make me blush. I'm just glad you enjoyed it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0048
rows.name:
Well, I should be getting back.
Thanks for the eats.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0049
rows.name: Shall we, Lieutenant?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0050
rows.name:
Yeah, we'd better go too.
This was really great, Lin—thanks.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0051
rows.name: Yeah, this was fun, Lin.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0052
rows.name: Indeed, it was a most enjoyable food ritual.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0053
rows.name: All right—good luck out there, guys![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0054
rows.name:
Elma, the analysis is just about finished.
Gather your team and get over here.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0055
rows.name: On our way.[ST:wait ]
